Title: [ANN] [VLR TOKEN] | VALOREM FOUNDATION | NICHE E-COMMERCE PLATFORM FOR THE 99%
Body: Exchanges, Business Rewards, Development & The Death of SpicePay https://advalorem.io/blog/2018/10/29/exchange-listings-application-updates-business-rewards-program-and-loss-of-spicepay  For Immediate Release: Exchanges, Business Rewards, Development & The Death of SpicePay  Dover, DEâ€Šâ€”â€ŠOctober 29th 2018.  Exchanges  Announcing the following Exchange Listings for the VLR Token: Token.Store & EtherDelta  Disclaimer: Please remember that while we are building our application the demand for the VLR is not certain and contains the risk of decline. Potential investors are strongly advised to consult their legal, tax and financial advisors before investing. The offering on this site is not to be used in jurisdictions where public solicitation of offerings are not permitted; it is solely your responsibility to comply with the laws and regulations of your country of residence. We are not responsible for losses incurred as a result of trading or investing in the VLR. Cryptocurrencies are speculative in nature and neither the Valorem Foundation nor its agents, members nor affiliates can be held liable for losses incurred by speculative activity. Valorem Foundation, Inc recognizes that the value of the VLR is purely tied to its utility and community support. Investments may lose value. FREE Business Rewards Program for Customer Retention  As we step into the next phase of our development, we have begun to identify the needs of our users and have begun to expand and grow new featuresâ€Šâ€”â€Šone such feature is:  Free Business Rewards Program for Customer Retention (REGISTRATON OPEN NOW!)  As we expand the FREE Business Rewards Program across the globe we have started to create a focus group with various businesses to help us perfect and improve this product. If anyone in our community is interested in helping us recruit businesses to our FREE Business Rewards Program, please sign up HERE. We will contact and onboard them.  Any business with a customer base can join this program to grow their customer base and differentiate themselves from the â€œSea of Marketing Emailsâ€ crowd. Onboarding is easy, when your customers checkout, we simply need an email address and we can immediately make them a VLR Token Reward Participant, allowing them to redeem their VLR for goods and services in your establishment, other establishments like yours that accept the VLR Reward Program, or sell it on an exchange.  Application Development Update: Public and Private Profile Pages  What developments are we working on?  Public and Private Profile Pagesâ€Šâ€”â€ŠOn these pages, users will display their details to the community. Details will include KYC verifications, personal descriptions, and services they are participating in on the Valorem platform.  Postingâ€Šâ€”â€ŠOn these pages the users will be able to see and participate in what the Valorem Community will offer with regard to Loans, Investments and Hedging and Trust Me.  After that we will develop the Chat functions, Announcements, and perfect the User Dashboard.  Once all these functions are running smoothly, we will implement the Loans, Investments and Hedging and Trust Me functions. All according to our Road Map.  Itâ€™s an exciting time for us as we begin marketing, growing and onboarding users for our various services.  Sign Up for Businesses & Individual Loans, Investments, Hedging & Trust Me.  Sign Up for for FREE Business Rewards Program. (REGISTRATION OPEN NOW!)  The Death of SpicePay  Earlier this month, we received the following email from the SpicePay team. Needless to say, we are very disappointed that we have spent time integrating with them and after all that they are going out of businessâ€Šâ€”â€Šjust one month later.  We have already removed the functionality for using SpicePay from our site and will continue to develop new forms of FIAT payments for the Valorem Platform through reliable merchants.  We will announce a new processor partner as soon as an agreement is reached.  AdValorem!

Author: ValoremFoundation
Title: [ANN] [VLR TOKEN] | VALOREM FOUNDATION | NICHE E-COMMERCE PLATFORM FOR THE 99%
Body: Development Updates for January 2019  Dear Valorem Community,  We are excited to say that we are slowly moving towards our goal of a fully functioning platform.  As foundation is the most important of a steady user experience, our first move was to create a simple and easy to use Profile Section for each user. Last week we made live a public and private profile update for every user.  â€”-  Update 1: The Public Profile Link on your user navigation take you to a Public url link that each user can share with others. This is helpful for each user when you want to someone outside the application (or inside) to see your Bio (About Me), Reviews (USER REVIEWS), Active Platform Posts (ACTIVE POSTS), Posts Your Shared with Others (SHARED POSTS) & Completed Transactions (COMPLETED POSTS); as well as KYC status on the application. This section will be updated with transactions that each user personally participates in the future.  This update is now Live! The link to it can be found here:  Update 2: The Private Profile Link on your user navigation takes you to a similar page as above where you can enter your personal information, update your picture that feeds to the public page.  In the private page, we show you some personal details that does not get shared on the public page, like your phone number and your token balance.  This update is now Live! The link to it can be found here:  Private Profile on Valorem Foundation Application Private Profile on Valorem Foundation Application  Update 3: The most common element between users is their email address. As the functions of the platform expand we want people to start using each otherâ€™s email addresses to send tokens to each other.  For this reason, we have created a feature where you can use a â€œknownâ€ email address of a known user to send VLR token to them instead of long and complicated Eth Addresses.  This update is now Live! See below.  The features above are commonly used when the users are aware of each otherâ€™s intentions and needs with regard to the application. That is why we are currently working on implementing the following changes in the coming months that will take us  a giant leap closer to a complete user experience.  Once completed, we will load the financial features of the application.  Next updates will include:  Posting - Where every user can see and participate in a Forum/Discussion Page like environment. Select products and services, interact with others.  Secure Messaging/Chat Feature allowing interaction between users so they can arrange, discuss and plan on how to process the various Loans/Investments/Trust Me/Hedge based transactions.  As a replacement for our loss of our processor SpicaPay, we have found a replacement and actively seeing how we can integrate with them. The functional processor will allow us to connect all global users under one Valorem Application. Stay tuned for more updates on this in the coming months as well.  We are currently in discussions with a few exchanges and should have a few new listings shortly. Stand by for more on this in the coming weeks.  Valorem Team  https://advalorem.io/blog/2019/1/12/development-updates-for-january-2019

Author: ValoremFoundation
Title: [ANN] [VLR TOKEN] | VALOREM FOUNDATION | NICHE E-COMMERCE PLATFORM FOR THE 99%
Body: For Immediate Release: Valorem Foundation, Inc partners with SpicePay to be able to process credit and debits card payments on their financial environment platform that is currently in development.  Dover, DE - August 25th 2018.  Valorem Foundation, Inc today announced a collaboration agreement with SpicePay, a payment processing software build on three basic principles: speed, safety, and personalized approach.  SpicePay adds the following benefits to the Valorem Foundation's Platform.  Speed: Merchants in the EU can access funds in less than 24 hours, as opposed to 72 hours with traditional payment processing.  Safety via SSL: Transaction processes are carried out using a secured connection through HTTPS protocol with 128 bytes encryption of transferred data, which bars any possibility of third-party data interception.  Personal approach: A level of personal service and complete support, unusual in our industry. Unlike financial institutions, SpicePay does not sort users by any criteria and strives to provide every customer with the same quality service.  You can view a full list of all the benefits of using SpicePay: The SpicePay Difference.  â€œWe are delighted to partner with SpicePay to create a fair and secure exchange for KYC vetted transactions bridging the mainstream with crypto. Valorem Foundation's mission is to develop a complete and sustainable financial ecosystem and we trust SpicePay can help us get there. After many conversations with SpicePayâ€™s team we have confidence that they will be a solid partner on our journey to create a simple and easy-to-use financial network on the blockchain. We look forward to expanding our partnership as much as possible in the near future. Together, SpicePay and Valorem Foundation will use their technology to combat the risks of todayâ€™s volatile cryptocurrency markets and provide a trusted platform for those who wish to see this market flourish and develop into the next big wave!â€ said Val Kleyman, Founder and CEO of Valorem Foundation.  Valorem Foundation, is developing a community peer-to-peer platform for multi-party transactions. It is a blockchain-based platform that allows users to exchange value via smart contracts. Once on the platform, users will be able to borrow, lend, invest, transfer, hedge others and exchange value between each other using the VLR (our token and method of transacting), creating a trust-based platform that removes the need for 3rd-party services or external vendors.  Valorem Foundation has already launched the following updates for their program located on their new subdomain located at ico.advalorem.io.  User enabled multi-purpose wallets able to hold Bitcoin, Ethereum, purchase and hold VLR tokens.  Transaction visibility and 0% fee transfers of VLR when transferring inside the environment.  Support functions and password systems.  Troubleshooting and system integrity maintenance.  A note on getting listed on exchanges:  â€œWe have been contacted by various exchanges," says Mr. Kleyman. "However, before any listing takes place, it must be in the interest of all the people who are a part of our community. We will announce a listing agreement once we have finished our due diligence on these potential future partners.â€  The following is a list of items currently in development by Valorem Foundation:  Implementation of SpicePay for users to be able to purchase VLR via credit/debit card (additional KYC will be required).  Public forum style community chat and deal proposals.  Private style chat between two users for private deal finalization.  The following are the services that Valorem is planning on rolling out later this year:  â€œLending smart contractâ€ development with hedge voting and reserve.  â€œInvesting smart contractâ€ development with hedge voting and reserve.  â€œTrust Meâ€ by Valorem Foundation - a user to user exchange using smart contracts in order to safely and securely transact between unknown parties using an escrow function on the platform. This service is designed primarily to build trust between users who don't know each other.  We will provide more updates on the smart contracts and specific ecosystem tools as they become available in the near future.  For more information about Valorem Foundation Inc please visit their website at www.advalorem.io.

Author: ValoremFoundation
Title: [ANN] [VLR TOKEN] | VALOREM FOUNDATION | NICHE E-COMMERCE PLATFORM FOR THE 99%
Body: Dear Investors & Valorem Foundation Members,   Thank you everyone who participated in our ICO.   What an amazing experience doing an ICO. We've made amazing partners, friends and collaborators. We have reached the far corners of the blockchain industry and we are just warming up!   With only 1 day left until we close our ICO, we want to thank everyone who contributed, participated and supported our plans to build something truly unique and valuable for the blockchain industry for the long term.  While other ICO's promise the world and do not deliver, the end of our ICO is just the first step for the Valorem Foundation.   We know the ICO industry has suffered major setbacks. However, the Valorem Foundation is still going strong and working to fulfill the promises it made 6 months ago. We appreciate your patience and support in our initiatives.  Over the last 2 months, we have been developing a simple and easy to use dashboard with 4 wallets: BTC, ETH, VLR & USD. We are proud to say that our wallets are almost complete and we will be sending out invites to all participants within the next 30 days.   The Valorem Team is comprised of builders and after we launch the wallets, we will begin to onboard users, vendors and participants to begin using the basic platform.   Once we our environment is stabilized and growing, we will begin developing our lending and investing smart contracts. Here we will truly stand out from the crowd and build something that is of value and can be utilized in a multi-faceted approach - to reach everyone!  Current Stats & Highlights:  12,000+ Twitter followers 15,000+ Telegram members 60,000+ Email subscribers 40,000,000+ VLR Tokens Reserved and Awaiting Allocation  When will we be listed on exchanges?   We are aware of this need, we are in touch with a number of exchange platforms and are reviewing them. While we know the benefit of going on an exchange, we are bound by the rules of our SAFT and our PPM. As soon as we will get listed on any exchange we will let our community know. Until then, your tokens will be safely stored in your wallets or outside them (if that is what you decide to do once you are registered.)  It is and will always be our goal to stabilize the value of the VLR and to grow the community. Thank you for being part of this journey with us.  Stay tuned! The best is yet to come!    Let's Invest AdValorem!  Regards,  Valorem Foundation Team https://advalorem.io/blog/the-best-is-yet-to-come

Author: ValoremFoundation
Title: [ANN] [VLR TOKEN] | VALOREM FOUNDATION | NICHE E-COMMERCE PLATFORM FOR THE 99%
Body: WELCOME TO THE VALOREM FOUNDATION!  Thank You for Participating in the Valorem Foundation VLR Token Sale.  Does anyone know why Bitcoin and other crypto's fluctuate so much? It's no secret that a few wallet's control their market value.  Well, with over 53,000+ participants in the Valorem Foundation ICO, it's almost impossible to have that kind of control over our VLR Token value. That is what makes it so special.  Valorem Foundation Leadership has decided early on that community is more important than whales. So, we let the whales be where they belong... ...out in the sea.  We are only looking to build and support the community that's entrusting us.  Quick Note: Thank you for opening and reading our newsletter. We know you don't always do that, but please remember, for a user to get the Airdrop, you must be on our newsletter list and actively reading our communications. This way we remove all the fake email addresses and make sure that the tokens we will send, really will go to someone who will use them. Any emails that bounce or unsubscribe will not receive the Airdrop.  IMPORTANT NOTICE  After completing the purchase/transfer, please remember to send an additional email confirmation to Foundation@AdValorem.io within 24 hours of initiating the transfer.  Upon receipt of the funds, we will confirm your purchase and send you an Electronic SAFT document to sign and approve.  Once SAFT is Signed, please go to www.MyEtherWallet.com, create your Ethereum Wallet, then email us the Ether Wallet Address so we may document where to send your VLR Tokens after the crowdsale is finished and the platform is launched.  When the ICO is finished and the Platform is launched, we will send you an invitation email where you can claim your tokens.  ACCREDITED INVESTORS ONLY  www.advalorem.io

Body: Everyone always talks about the competition. Weâ€™ve evaluated lots of â€œwould-beâ€ competitors. Like SALT.  However SALT ioperates on a membership basis. Meaning, that the tokens you buy with salt and trade on the exchanges are not the same token you use on their platform. That is a big difference to what we are offering. With us, the tokens that you buy use directly on the platform. Remember, Disrupt and Simplify. To keep it simple, you WILL want to hold them and use them because they will allow you to invest in many different things, creating passive income and new opportunities. Salt is a great product, but our scale will really Disrupt and Simplify things.

Title: [ANN] [VLR TOKEN] | VALOREM FOUNDATION | NICHE E-COMMERCE PLATFORM FOR THE 99%
Body: Great question. Yes, each loan category/transaction will be a seperate contract. The terms of each loan will depend on the creator of the loan and the borrower. Percentages will vary and amounts will vary. Think of it as going to book an Airbnb. The host posts a property, sets the price, description, etc and a guests pays the price. The host getâ€™s to accept a certain type of guest (high trust level for example). And they both build their own reputation with reviews. Same here, the more payments and transactions a user does, the more their trust level builds and the more they can do on the platform. Take a look at our UI. It will explain it in more detail. https://vimeo.com/245429073

Author: ValoremFoundation
Title: [ANN] [VLR TOKEN] | VALOREM FOUNDATION | NICHE E-COMMERCE PLATFORM FOR THE 99%
Body: Thats a great question too! Letâ€™s keep this going. We love the participation. Please make sure you join our social media groups including Telegram and all the others on the bottom of our homepage: www.advalorem.io  Now to answer the question: when the correction to Bitcoin and all other cryptocurrencies happen Bitcoin and many others will fall. In an unregulated market like this corrections have great swings.  Overtime, the market will he overtaken by value adding projects such as ours and the swings will he less volatile.  However, the key feature of our project is not the stabilization of value of BTC it is the stable and single growing value of VLR. Our token will grow simply by all the enhanced features we plan to add to it.  Our value will come from more buyers than sellers. More people will want to stay on the platform than leave it.  We hope we answered your question, please let us know if you want more clarity on this.  Thanks

Happy Holidays from the Valorem Foundation!  ---  Dear Valorem Team and Bounty Hunters, Today is Really Exciting for us! We have completely revamped the Bonus and Timeline!  Currently, and for the next 44 days we are in Pre-Sale Mode and the Bonus is 100%.  Yes, that's right. For every (1) Ether you put in, you will get 2000 VLR tokens. You will be able to use them in the platform when we roll it out.  The new timeline is currently on the website: www.advalorem.io  Minimum 0.1 ETH for Pre-Sale and ICO  Now thru Jan 28th - Pre-Sale Mode - 100% Bonus (This is the time to buy our token) VLR Token is Live! - January 28th ICO - 50% Bonus February 28th ICO - 40% Bonus March 28th ICO - 20% Bonus April 28th ICO - 10% Bonus May 28th ICO - 5% Bonus June 28th ICO - Closes  We want to build a big community of users in our new platform. Author: Coin_trader
Title: [ANN] [VLR TOKEN] | VALOREM FOUNDATION | NICHE E-COMMERCE PLATFORM FOR THE 99%
Body: Is it another lending platform or just a platform that helping the users to find someone he needed to make a loan? And what are the methods you'll be using to be sure that the one making a loan will pay his obligations and will not run with his loan?

Author: ValoremFoundation
Title: [ANN] [VLR TOKEN] | VALOREM FOUNDATION | NICHE E-COMMERCE PLATFORM FOR THE 99%
Body: Great question. Yes this is a lending platform and it will help users find someone that needs a loan. The interesting portion to your question is the way we do our Reserve Lending process. A portion of the loan is held until the Trust level of the user goes up. After it does a portion of the loan is released until it's fully funded. Checkout our Pitch Deck/Whitepaper on the website. They really explain that in detail. There is also a hedge that is supported. Essentially guaranteeing 100% of the loan.  However, we are not just a lending platform. Since that is just one smart contract. The lending concept is the "brains" behind this platform's lending portion. It's truly unique in the way it works. Take a look at the video too, it goes over it in a general way. https://vimeo.com/237673271
